cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper deals with video analysis and activity recognition, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The focus on egocentric perspective and fine-grained discrimination suggests a potential fit with multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-categories.
